parameters:
One-armed Opro: What an awful face... Have you been chased
by a demon, miss?

Clea: Since my parents were killed, I have only lived with
the thought of killing dragons.

Clea: The only fear I have felt... is the fear of not being
able to avenge my parents.

Clea: ...It shouldn't have happened! And yet, when I
confronted the ogre, I trembled in fear!

Clea: Why... \| Even though I've become fearless...! It's
scary... To die... To fight... I'm scared... \| Why?!

One-armed Opro: That's just who you are, a cowardly and
fearful little girl... What are you surprised about... It's
normal.

One-armed Opro: Just live according to your parents' will
and be happy... That's the normal way of living, isn't it?
Clea: Why do you fight, Opro-san...?

One-armed Opro: That's a story from when I still had both
hands... We traveled throughout the empire while chasing our
dreams.

One-armed Opro: One day, I encountered an ogre and in an
instant, I lost my arm and many of my comrades.

One-armed Opro: Because of the promise with my friends and
because living means fighting.
Clea: You don't feel any fear...?

One-armed Opro: It's not that I don't feel it... I know true
fear.

One-armed Opro: Continuing revenge means living on edge,
being alert to every sound and presence.

One-armed Opro: Your small shoulders carry a heavy burden...
Even if you run away, no one will blame you.

One-armed Opro: Well, it's best to rest here until morning.
Tell me where the ogre is when you wake up.
One-armed Opro: The ogre has been our prey for a long time.
